* {{cite book|year=1957年|title_zh=《語言學的論文》|title=''Essays in Linguistics''|url=https://archive.org/details/essaysinlinguist00gree|publisher=Chicago: University of Chicago Press}}
* {{cite book|year=1963年|title="Some universals of grammar with particular reference to the order of meaningful elements," in ''Universals of Language''|url=https://archive.org/details/universalsoflang00gree|pages=[https://archive.org/details/universalsoflang00gree/page/73 73]–113|publisher=Cambridge: MIT Press}}
